node.text:
Later today Mercury our planet of the mind will shift into the diplomatic, beauty loving Libra. 

Mercury determines the way we think, how we articulate information and how we communicate with ourselves and others. 

As Mercury enters into the balanced sign of Libra we feel a harmonious shift, that brings us lessons on how we can look at all perspectives and be a little more mindful of one another’s circumstances. 

Libra is ruled by Venus, the planet of love and the divine feminine, with this energy coming together with our goddess energy of our sun in Virgo, this is a time to really embody your femininity ~ be soft, flow with the wind, have deep intimate conversations, spend your time with the amazing women around you, love and be love.

These wounds may come up as flash backs of bad memories, you may feel just off and distant. This is a time for you to do some deep healing, slow down and feel into what's coming up for you. or'.

node.text:
Venus Opposite Chiron at 12°
Venus in our planet of love, relationships and all intimate partnerships. Chiron is the asteroid of deep wounds and is one of the biggest spiritual teachers in astrology. Chiron illuminates your wounds, to show you where healing needs to be done. 

This alignment can be really tough to navigate through as it highlights wounds within relationships that have yet to be healed. These can be painful to relive and can bring up feelings you didn’t realise at the time. But ultimately you can turn these into lessons to help heal those wounds and move forward from the past.

Journal prompt for today:
The emotions and pain that have been coming up for me recently are trying to tell me that…

May be an image of text that says 'Mercury our planet of the mind is currently opposing Neptune our planet of spirit and the subconscious. This alignment can bring miscommunications, difficulty focusing and leaving your thoughts foggy and scattered. Take your time and slow down to process through things. Channelling these anxieties and emotions into a creative outlet can help you to feel grounded and clarity. This 1S the time to be kind to yourself, let yourself relax, refresh, rest and put trust in your intuition. sistersvillage'.

node.text:
Mercury in Virgo opposite Neptune in Pisces and is currently at its peak today at 22°

This alignment also heightens messages from spirit and messages in dreams. Try and journal down your dreams as soon as you wake up and then come back to these over the next few weeks to decipher. 

Neptune is still currently in retrograde which influence has been shining light onto things that have been going on in the shadows and breaking down those perfect illusions around us. This retrograde has been and still is working to wake us up to what’s really been happening around us. 

Today’s journal prompt:
What do I need to feel safe in this exact moment? Can I give this to myself?

The Moon is currently in the dreamy sign of Pisces, this shift heightens your emotions, sensitives and illusions. This time is all about connecting with your spirituality and the you within even deeper - the soul beyond the physical body.

Ride the wave, go with your own divine flow, be present, meditate, star gaze and take a long bath. This is the time for deep reflection over the insights that came through for you over the weekends Full Moon in Aquarius, be still with all that you are feeling at the moment.

node.text:
Full Moon in Aquarius 𖡼 August 22
This is our second Full Moon in Aquarius for the year, which very rarely happens making this full moon extra special and super magical. 

This Full Moon in Aquarius illuminates the things, situations and people that we just need to be free from. It’s time to move forward, it’s time for you to purge and release, for you to expand. 

This is a time to revisit the themes that have been coming up for you over the past month. Have you been listening to those whispers within or have you been distracting yourself from what needs to happen? 

Falling on the last day of Leo season at 29° this represents an end of a cycle, a chapter of your life coming to a close. Self awareness is heightened, really feel into the insights that are flowing through right now. 

Journal prompt for Full Moon in Aquarius:
What type of person do I want to be?
Write down everything from the personality traits you want to embody, the goals you want to have achieved, the habits you want to have, your routine, how you feel, who you are surrounded by, as many details as possible. 

If you would like more info on this Full Moon, including a Full Moon ritual and mantra, an oracle spread plus more info on the Full Moon and the planetary influences for the month of August you can download my monthly energetics guide through the website.

Uranus has the power to create massive changes for our future. Uranus is a foward thinking planet, itis it is the planet of innovation and collective awakening. This retrograde is guiding you within, asking us to look at the changes that have happened to our society over the past year, giving us the time to reflect on what has changed within us and what new perspectives we have gained over this time.'.

node.text:
Uranus Retrograde ❊
Uranus will station retrograde 3 hours from now and will be retrograde up until mid January of next year. 

This movement is here to awaken us as a collective, to guide us within to reflect on the things that have happened to our community and the world as a whole over this past year and how that has changed us as human beings. 

Uranus currently resides in the grounded and practical sign of Taurus. Uranus in Taurus influences us to reevaluate what we hold our value and worth in, especially when it comes to holding your worth in how much money you have or what material items you have. Over these next few years this transit is here to teach you that no material success or possession is ever more valuable than human connections. 

Journal prompt for today:
How have my perspectives shifted during this past year, how have I changed?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Amy 𓇸 𖤓 • Empowering Astrology on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Mercury in Virgo open communication, create routine, organise and declutter'.

node.text:
Mercury enters Virgo ☿ 
Mercury is the planet of our mind, it determines the way we think, how we articulate information and how we communicate with ourselves and others. ⁣
⁣
As Mercury enters into the precise and organised sign of Virgo we feel a shift guiding us towards sorting out our lives, clearing the junk, the mental chatter and to get really intentional about what we are focusing our energy on. 

Mercury is at home in the sign of Virgo, so this shift is definitely a positive one. This is a time for authentic communication, express your thoughts openly and honestly. Create a balanced daily routine. Organise and declutter your space, your mind and your life. 

Today’s journal prompt: 
Where in my life do I need more structure?

This is the portal that is held within the star Sirius (the brightest star in the nights sky, known as the gateway to the spirit realm) as the sun reaches its mid way point in the sign of Leo. This is a powerful day to manifest all of your intentions, dreams and desires. with love, sistersvillage'.

node.text:
88 activation 𓄂 Happy New Moon and Lionsgate portal, today is such a powerful day energetically. Can you feel it?

The Lionsgate portal is held within the star Sirius (the brightest star in the nights sky, known as the gateway to the spirit realm) and reaches peak activation as the sun hits its mid way point in the sign ruled by the Lion, Leo - which is where the name lionsgate comes from. 

In numerology 8 is the number of wholeness and abundance. This potent energy is the perfect day to manifest all of your intentions and desires. 

Ritual for lionsgate portal + New Moon in Leo
Write down where you want your life to be a year from now, but write it as if it’s happening now, how you feel, how grateful you are for all that your life is, write as much detail as you can, every little thing you want to have in your life. 

Feel into your words, into the feeling of having all of these dreams and desires. Then sleep with these words under your pillow tonight, envisioning yourself and your life as what you’ve written as you begin to fall asleep 𖤓

This time is so beyond powerful, bringing our self awareness to an even deeper level. This awareness illuminates old wounds and patterns, which can be confronting and uncomfortable, but remember that expansion and growth comes from the discomfort. Honour what you have been through, but don't let it hold you back. It's time to enter a new chapter of life. sistersvillage sistersvi love'.

node.text:
New Moon in Leo 8/8 𓄂
New Moons birth the beginning of a New Lunar cycle, they are a cosmic reset. This is a time to honour the things we have gone through and then begin setting new intentions and goals. 

This is the time to be courageous, be playful, have fun, express yourself authentically and flow into wherever this path is taking you. Put your trust in the universe and know that everything is unfolding exactly how it is meant to.

If you would like more information on how you can work with the energetics of this New Moon plus a how to manifestation ritual you can download my August Energetics guide which you can find on my website under the guides and ebooks section •

node.text:
Sun Square Uranus ❊
Uranus is our planet of awakening, this transit gives you valuable insights on how different your life could be if you pushed forward and took the risks. 

These insights may come through in many different ways, be open to signs and tap into those feelings that are coming up for you. 

It’s time to break free from trying to fit in, trying to keep yourself small. Get out of your comfort zone, liberate yourself, express yourself freely and begin living the life that you deserve. 

Journal prompt for today:
In what ways have I been unauthentic? Why was this?

Beautiful art by @lilly_prinz
